Indian media is so partial towards Himachal. Whenever it comes to pahadi folk culture, Indian media never goes to Himachal. Whereas Himachal has given the country so many legendary singers like, Mohit Chauhan, Baba Hansraj Raghuwanshi, Karnail Rana, Kuldeep. There are so many folk artists like Mahendro Singh and Veena, Roshan Lal.
@CokeStudioBharat show some love for Himachal.
